lockquote><br />\n可以戴住眼鏡做個test？</blockquote><br />\nGFS 同 class 1 都得<br />\n但 GFS 戴咗都好撚難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打網上有冇d sample 試下？6米睇幾細嘅字？2cm x 2cm？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細過你去眼鏡鋪驗眼最後一行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞇起隻眼想睇清 D 就屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔駛問咁多架喇巴打, 就算我話你一定睇唔到, 你都係會報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左眼perfect，右眼50度散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n散光仲麻撚煩過近視<br />\n近視你偷雞瞇眼都仲睇到<br />\n散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇吓你會唔會特登配散光鏡去驗眼囉<br />\n可能唔差太遠, 但如果去到即場驗眼係差少少就戇鳩<br />\n不過就算過到眼, 後面都好多關<br />\n機師 post 雖然成功率低 (~0.1%), 但勝在如果你真係合適嘅話, 真係好大機會<br />\n而如果你真係唔合適, 你有鷹眼都係 foul <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1231cd95a3d0d051d1c9897f82ac44da1c5f6fcc","tid":173054,"uid":7155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無近視無帶眼鏡但有色弱係咪都係唔會收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有色弱100%唔得，連民航機機師都唔得"},{"pid":"8e92fe1ff5289532019832b2338fcd601dd35f92","tid":173054,"uid":88206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上次in比考官話睇唔到有passion/dedication<br />\n屌佢老尾點先算有passion</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPrelim定Panel?</blockquote><br />\n同問<br />\n<br />\nprelim同panel啲官都唔似咁得閒去寸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能巴打表現好到人地想收, 但passion方面唔夠, 所以先直接講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b616d031ed20bea12dcdecdaf939789e7898a1da","tid":173054,"uid":73410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blo